      "path": "artifacts/projects/default_project/output/app/README.md",
      "content": "# HR System Prototype\n\nThis is a simple prototype web application for the HR System project.\n\n## Features\n- Employee Management\n- Payroll\n- Attendance\n- Recruitment\n- Training\n- Performance Evaluation\n\n## Users\n- HR Staff\n- Managers\n- Regular Employees\n\n## Security\n- Privacy compliance\n- Data encryption\n- Role-based access control\n\n## Integration\n- Payroll system\n- Attendance system\n- Training platforms\n\n## UI\n- Multi-language support (Arabic and English)\n- User-friendly interface\n\n## How to Run\n\n1. This is a static web application.\n2. Open the `index.html` file in any modern web browser.\n3. Use the language selector dropdown to switch between Arabic and English.\n\n## Notes\n- This is a prototype and does not include backend or real data.\n- No actual integration or security features are implemented.\n\n---\n\n### Run Instructions\n\n- Simply open `index.html` in your browser.\n- No installation or server setup required.\n\n### Prototype Disclaimer\nThis application is a prototype for demonstration purposes only and is not production-ready.\n## تشغيل سريع على Windows\n- Double click `open_app.bat` لو التطبيق static HTML فقط.\nهذا Prototype أولي مبني من المتطلبات، وليس نظام Production كامل.\n",
